    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the pavement today. I\u2019ve loved driving this, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
