    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a longitudinal 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, providing the precise kinemantics and tactile feedback expected of this chassis. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and high-pressure VANOS performance remain sharp, making this a turn-key performance machine.",
